text: Centrinaspis elegans is a species of true weevils in the subfamily Curculioninae. It is found in Brazil. The type specimen was collected in Chapada Campo. == References == == External links == * * Centrinaspis elegans at insectoid.info * Centrinaspis elegans at collections.si.edu Category:Beetles described in 1922 Category:Curculioninae Category:Insects of Brazil
